Since establishment in the year 1995, we, Ahuja Products, are consistently working with an aim of designing and manufacturing the finest quality electric products and components. We are a renowned manufacturer of this respective arena and are committed to offer top-quality electric solutions. Our offered range encompasses quality-approved range of Line Testers, Electric Door Bells, Power Strips, Bulkheads Fittings, Electrical Holder, Foot Lights and Down Light Frame, Multi Plug, Metal Clamp, Metal and Tube Clip and MCB Box. All of our offered products are made of superior grade raw material procured from reliable vendors, which make them perfect and highly efficient for heavy duty usage. Our entire range is well known for their low maintenance, stylish look and durability. In addition to this, the products are available in various shapes, sizes and designs which are developed keeping in mind the varied requirements of our respected customers. Moreover, we stay in close coordination with our clients as it helps us to build healthy and long standing relationship with them.
With rock solid determination and capable guidance of our respected mentor, Mr. Narendra Ahuja , our organization has grown from strength to strength and has achieved a dominating position in the market. He constantly guides us on the way of excellence with his remarkable domain expertise and immense knowledge.
